msgstr "你的交易已成功完成。Token 將很快儲值到你的帳號。"

msgid "Continue"
msgstr "繼續"

msgid "I'm ChatBudgie, your AI assistant. How can I help you today?"
msgstr "我是 ChatBudgie，你的 AI 助手。今天有什麼可以幫你？"

msgid "Preparing index"
msgstr "正在準備索引"

msgid "Indexing content"
msgstr "正在索引內容"

