msgstr "你們提供哪些服務？"

msgid "We offer AI chatbot solutions that help you automate support and engage your visitors."
msgstr "我們提供 AI 聊天機器人解決方案，協助你自動化支援並與訪客互動。"

msgid "Is my data safe?"
msgstr "我的資料安全嗎？"

msgid "Oops! Something went wrong."
msgstr "糟糕！出了點問題。"

msgid "I'm having a little trouble thinking right now. Please try again in a moment."
msgstr "我現在思考時遇到一點困難。請稍後再試。"

msgid "Try Again"
msgstr "再試一次"

msgid "Ask anything..."
msgstr "隨便問..."

